This product highlight presentation was recorded during the congatec press conference at the Embedded World trade show on Feb. 23, 2016. It covers the COM Express and industrial Thin Mini-ITX products based on the new Intel® Core™, Celeron® and Xeon® Processors (Intel codename "Sylake”). Some of the products also feature the latest Intel® Iris Pro graphics for enhanced visual performance.
The presentation also covers the easy integrable COM Express module conga-TR3 based on AMD R- & G-Series SOC with error code corrected DDR4  RAM for high reliable operation.
These high performance products allow for easy integration to embedded systems and provide an almost infinite upgrade path for upcoming processor technologies.

Speaker: Martin Danzer, Director Product Management, congatec AG